75  bool FrameIChannel::GetData(SeqViewDouble& rSeqView) {
76  bool status = true;
77 
78  if (mFrameVect != NULL) {
79  FrVectFree(mFrameVect);
80  mFrameVect = NULL;
81  }
82  while (ReopenIfModified());
83  mFrameVect = FrFileIGetVectDN(miFile, const_cast<char *> (mChannelName.c_str()), mStartTime, mDataLength);
84  if (mFrameVect == NULL) {

87  std::string emsg = s.str();
88  LogSevere("%s", emsg.c_str());
89  mStartTime += mDataLength;
90  throw std::runtime_error(emsg);
91  }
92  Dmatrix* data = rSeqView.GetData();
93 
94  if (mFrameVect->next == NULL) {
95  // No missed data
96  if ((data->size1() != 1) || (data->size2() != mFrameVect->nx[0])) {
97  data->resize(1, mFrameVect->nData);
98  }
99  PushFrVect(mFrameVect, *data, 0, 0.0, 1.0);
100  } else {
101  // Missed data
102  status = false;
103  if ((data->size1() != 2) || (data->size2() != mFrameVect->nx[0])) {
104  data->resize(2, mFrameVect->nData);
105  }
106  PushFrVect(mFrameVect, *data, 0, 0.0, 1.0);
107  PushFrVect(mFrameVect->next, *data, 0, 0.0, 1.0);
108  }
109  rSeqView.SetStart(mStartTime);
110  rSeqView.SetSampling(mFrameVect->dx[0]);
111  rSeqView.SetScale(1.0);

114  }

143  void FrameIChannel::PushFrVect(FrVect *frv, Dmatrix& data, unsigned int row, double offset, double slope) {
144  switch (frv->type) {
145  case FR_VECT_C:
